    <section class="grid" aria-label="Introduction">

      <article class="card">
        <h2>What is Lampadēphóros?</h2>
        <p>
          Lampadēphóros means “torchbearer”. We create content that doesn’t need to shout
          in order to shine: calm, clear, deep — without fear.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Why do we exist?</h2>
        <p>
          Because many people are searching for meaning — but are tired of noise, conflict, and shallow hype.
          We want to build a space where you can breathe.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Our goal</h2>
        <p>
          To carry light forward: through films, chapters, impulses, and behind-the-scenes work —
          and later also through pilgrimages, workshops, and talks.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>How we work</h2>
        <p>
          Step by step. Foundation first, expansion second: clean structure, logical order,
          strong visuals, and words that hold weight.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>What we stand for</h2>
        <p>
          Stillness over noise. Depth over posing. Truth over effect. Beauty that opens,
          not manipulates.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Join / Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Want to collaborate, share an idea, or ask about an offer? Write to us — we’ll reply.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:lampadephoros.media@gmail.com">Email us →</a>
      </article>

